sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant API as DS Pipelines API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant S3 as S3 Object Store<br/>9000/TCP or 443/TCP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant WFC as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant Pod as Pipeline Pod<br/>(launcher/driver)
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC

    Note over User, S3: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission (External User)
    User->>Router: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Router->>OAuth: Forward (Reencrypt)<br/>Port 8443
    OAuth->>API: Proxied request<br/>Port 8888, TLS (PodToPodTLS)
    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>MySQL, TLS (PodToPodTLS)<br/>Username/Password
    API->>S3: Store pipeline artifacts<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>S3 Access Key/Secret Key
    S3-->>API: Upload confirmed
    DB-->>API: Metadata stored
    API-->>OAuth: Success response
    OAuth-->>Router: Proxied response
    Router-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over K8s, MLMD: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution (Argo Workflow)
    API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>WFC: Workflow event
    WFC->>K8s: Create Pipeline Pods<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>Pod: Pod scheduled
    Pod->>API: gRPC calls<br/>Port 8887, TLS (PodToPodTLS)
    Pod->>MLMD: Log artifacts/executions<br/>Port 8080 gRPC, TLS (PodToPodTLS)
    Pod->>S3: Read/Write artifacts<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>S3 Access Key/Secret Key
    S3-->>Pod: Artifact data
    MLMD-->>Pod: Metadata recorded

    Note over User, K8s: Flow 3: DSPA Reconciliation (Operator)
    participant DSPO as DSPO Controller
    DSPO->>K8s: Watch DSPA CRs<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>DSPO: DSPA event
    DSPO->>DB: Health check<br/>MySQL TLS<br/>Username/Password
    DB-->>DSPO: Healthy
    DSPO->>S3: Health check<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>S3 credentials
    S3-->>DSPO: Healthy
    DSPO->>K8s: Deploy/update components<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
